ic German|Alemannic]]), '''Limig''' (German; archaic), '''[[:de:Limmat|Limmat]]''' (German, Romansh), '''Limmig''' (Aargau dialect), '''Lindimacus''' and '''Lindimagus''' (Latin; 8th-9th century), '''Lindmagt'''/'''Lindmat''' (German; 15th-16th century).,<ref>Albrecht Greule: ''Vor- und frühgermanische Flussnamen am Oberrhein. Ein Beitrag zur Gewässernamengebung des Elsass, der Nordschweiz und Südbadens.'' Winter, Heidelberg 1973, pp.&nbsp;129–132.</ref> '''[[:de:Linth|Linth]]''' (German; upper course) |- | [[Lippe (river)|Lippe]] | {{flagicon|GER}} | '''[[:de:Lippe (Fluss)|Lippe]]''' (German), '''Lupia''', '''Lippa''', '''Libia''' (Latin)<ref name=Gr/> |- | [[Livenza]] | {{flagicon|ITA}} | '''Lighintha''' (local Friulian),<ref>[http://www.arlef.it/it/documenti/#/toponomastica Toponomastica: denominazioni ufficiali in lingua friulana]</ref> '''Liquentia''', '''Liguencia''' or '''Liquetia''' (Latin),<ref name=Gr/> '''[[:fur:Livence|Livence]]''' (Friulian), '''[[:vec:Łivensa|Łivensa]]''' (Venetian), '''[[:it:Livenza|Livenza]]''' (Italian) |- | [[Ljubljanica]] | {{flagicon|SVN}} | '''[[:de:Ljubljanica|Laibach]]''' (German), '''[[:sl:Ljubljanica|Ljubljanica]]''' (Slovene, Croatian), '''[[:sk:Ľubľana|Ľubľanica]]''' (Slovak), '''[[:cs:Lublaňka|Lublaňka]]''' or '''Lublanice''' (Czech), '''[[:it: Ljubljanica|Lunghezza]]''' or '''Lubianizza''' (Italian), '''[[Nauportus]]''' - ''Ναύπορτος'' (Latin/Ancient Greek; 1st-century) |- | [[Ljungan]] | {{flagicon|SWE}} | '''Jångna''' or '''Aoa''' ([[Jamtlandic]]),<ref>{{cite book |last=Hellquist |first=Elof |title=Svensk etymologisk ordbok |year=1922 |publisher=Gleerups förlag |location=Stockholm |page=416}}</ref> '''[[:sv:Ljungan|Ljungan]]''' (Swedish), '''Ognar''' (Old Swedish; 15th century)<ref name=wahl>Wahlberg, Mats (2003): ''Svenskt ortnamnslexikon.'' Uppsala: Språk- och Folkminnesinst.</ref> |- | [[Ljusnan]] | {{flagicon|SWE}} | '''[[:sv:Ljusnan|Ljusnan]]''' (Swedish), '''Lusn''' (Old Swedish; 14th century)<ref name=wahl/> |- 